<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT69">
<l>cevikkiṉpa māvatuvuñ ceṅkaṇmāl nāmam</l>
<l>puvikkum puviyatuvē kaṇṭīr kavikku</l>
<l>niṟaiporuḷāy niṉṟāṉai nērpaṭṭēṉ pārkkil</l>
<l>maṟaipporuḷu mattaṉaiyē tāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Look, the name of the red-eyed Māl is what is bliss to the ears,</l>
<l>And it is the place [of refuge] for the [people of the] earth.</l>
<l>I have met [the Lord] who is the complete meaning of poetry.</l>
<l>If [we] look into [it], that much is the essence of the Vedas.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
